So here I am, back from no mans land.  Losing my mom fucked me up pretty bad, but I’m starting to feel better finally.  Feeling in a decent enough headspace to start making art again.  In order to start fresh I’m going to sell some pieces I have that I didn’t really make an effort to let go in the past. Some beads, pendants, marbles etc.  This is the first piece I’m offering up, a neat medium sized tile pendant.  DM with any inquiries and questions.  Cheers everyone, love you all 🖤
